These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, country, blues, funk, rock, house, trance
There are 7 different favourite colors: white, blue, purple, lilac, turquise, aquamarine, emerald
 1. the fan metal is between the fan funk and the fan trance##2
 2. the fan country is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 4. the fan rock is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes turquise##2
 5. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the fan funk##1
 7. the person who likes white is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes purple##2
 8. the person who likes blue is on the left of the fan trance##1
 9. the fan rock is on the left of the fan house##1
10. the fan rock is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
11. the fan house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | funk | metal | trance | country    | blues | rock   | house    |
| Color         | aquamarine  | blue   | lilac | white | purple   | emerald | turquise |

