.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, teacher, accountant, designer, electrician, engineer, journalist
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, sports, scientific, comedy, time-travel, documentary, adventure
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is between the engineer and the person watching documentary movies##2
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the journalist is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the teacher is in the middle##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the teacher##1
8. the electrician is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
9. the designer is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Job          | electrician | accountant | engineer | teacher | journalist | bartender      | designer  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | comedy  | adventure     | scientific     | time-travel  | martial-arts | sports |

