.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, chestnut, brown, mauve, ivory, amber, lavender
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: volleyball, weightlifting, basketball, badminton, snowboarding, surfing, water-polo
 1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who likes lavender##1
 4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who likes mauve##2
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Color   | lavender | ivory | fuchsia | chestnut   | mauve | brown | amber |
| Sport           | snowboarding | surfing     | weightlifting     | basketball | badminton   | volleyball   | water-polo    |

