.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  scientist, social-worker, security-guard, mechanic, designer, paramedic, musician
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, trance, reggae, dubstep, metal, punk, rock
 1. the musician is on the left of the fan reggae##1
 2. the designer is on the right of the fan metal##1
 3. the fan punk is on the right of the fan dubstep##1
 4. the designer is on the right of the fan metal##1
 5. the fan disco is on the right of the scientist##1
 6. the fan dubstep is between the security-guard and the fan punk##2
 7. the scientist is in the middle##1
 8. the fan dubstep is on the left of the mechanic##1
 9. the social-worker is the fan trance##1
10. the fan disco is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Job      | security-guard    | designer  | mechanic  | scientist  | musician      | paramedic       | social-worker |
| Music-Genre   | metal | dubstep | punk | rock | disco | reggae | trance  |

