The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, volleyball, baseball, climbing, parkour, snowboarding, cycling
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who growslily##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsdahlia##2
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who growsmarigold##1
9. the person who growsiris is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Flower   | marigold      | iris | dahlia | rose | bellflower      | lily      | amaryllis |
| Sport     | volleyball | snowboarding | cycling       | rugby | baseball | parkour | climbing |

