.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, billiard, mah-jongg, whist, go, monopoly
City: san-francisco, rome, marseilles, boston, liverpool, edinburgh, paris
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person playing whist##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing billiard is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to paris##2
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person playing go is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person playing whist##2
10. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Game   | scrabble | snooker    | mah-jongg | billiard   | go | monopoly    | whist |
| City      | boston | san-francisco | paris    | rome | liverpool    | marseilles | edinburgh  |

