 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
10. the gothic-revival house is between the modern house and the ranch-style house##2
11. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
