.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  engineer, bartender, doctor, fisherman, police-officer, accountant, firefighter
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, may, december, september, march, october, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the police-officer is in the middle##1
4. the engineer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the fisherman is between the person who's birthday is in march and the bartender##2
7. the accountant is between the doctor and the firefighter##2
8. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the bartender is on the left of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Job   | firefighter | accountant       | doctor    | police-officer | fisherman | bartender     | engineer       |
| Birthday   | may    | september | october | march        | december | january | june |

